1329","tid":1830181,"uid":27159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"雖然學歷都好緊要 <br />\n但係鄺仔真係勤力有恆心<br />\n考咁多次都無放棄<br />\n堅持考到合格<br />\n呢個恆心唔係人人有<br />\n真心respect"},{"pid":"68d664ff0af917dd87f3729766fc257e3a59a879","tid":1830181,"uid":49128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71a3313887d976cc5fb786846380a37e87b01329","tid":1830181,"uid":27159,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"雖然學歷都好緊要 <br />\n但係鄺仔真係勤力有恆心<br />\n考咁多次都無放棄<br />\n堅持考到合格<br />\n呢個恆心唔係人人有<br />\n真心respect"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"鄺仔加油"},{"pid":"a3f11351bb71c6b620f7c18f4cd677379a127aa0","tid":1830181,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:49:16.000Z","msg":"為梁義士而喊<br />\n佢係好人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa48f436207cf769814b7ab555d92524e5cc16d","tid":1830181,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"佢d標點俾人笑左好耐<br />\nbtw欣賞佢份人 同個高佬完全唔同做法"},{"pid":"bb4667d6aada382e66fc0600410f9b1804e1ce56","tid":1830181,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"8b0449dba7a233e387c99bb52231c9f561a649fc","tid":1830181,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"講真學歷係無意思"},{"pid":"11cdc095d9c6c5b467e8383ab9d52dba19880138","tid":1830181,"uid":172303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"做實事"},{"pid":"29c28ad1d18148e4fff5f9f2f8ce6310c8fdcc7e","tid":1830181,"uid":49128,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8b0449dba7a233e387c99bb52231c9f561a649fc","tid":1830181,"uid":154634,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"講真學歷係無意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T16:42:19.000Z","msg":"建制個班咪買番黎"},{